{"tid":836263,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"得罪講句 而家所有人都係廢柴","createTime":"2018-09-25T13:53:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T14:20:16.000Z","uid":187227,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d2ca0527664aa6d13eb1d3b3919892f323800883","tid":836263,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:53:06.000Z","msg":"仆街啦<br />\n想當年呀叔我要攞住支石矛去打獵<br />\n同啲長毛象打生打死先可以有野落肚<br />\n仲要鑽木取火先有啖熱野食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n邊似而家啲垃圾30後（1930）咁幸福有得用火水爐<br />\n仲有收音機聽 咁幸福都唔知怨咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a2bf763ba74af48d3995201c87b52f47b837d53","tid":836263,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"不服內辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f3aa0d801f6589ec019f09096528c2228cafec8","tid":836263,"uid":197452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"廢青"},{"pid":"859363a8be31a2177928d92200ff000dda15211f","tid":836263,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"廢柴不敢面對的真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55eeddfab4f9e3e38f58314ea20525cb560d6d36","tid":836263,"uid":187227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2f3aa0d801f6589ec019f09096528c2228cafec8","tid":836263,"uid":197452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"廢青"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-25T13:56:22.000Z","msg":"你再噪嘅話<br />\n我食完隻長毛象下一個就係你<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/tongue.png\" class=\"hkg